.l-default-container
  %section.p-user_details.l-single_container
    .p-user_detail-profile-box{style: 'background-image: url(/assets/common/user_bg.jpg)'}
      .p-user_detail-photo_box.u-taCenter
        = link_to '#' do
          .p-user_detail-photo{style: 'background-image: url(/assets/common/member_photo_noimage_thumb.png)'}
          %h2.p-user_detail-title.c-font-6
            マサ
        .p-user_detail-score.c-font-3
          %span 評価 11
          %span 出品数 14
    .u-bgWhite
      .p-user_detail-ratings-box.c-font-6
        %div
          .p-user_detail-ratings.l-clearfix
            %i.c-icon-good
            .u-taCenter.p-user_detail-ragtings-score
              11
        %div
          .p-user_detail-ratings.l-clearfix
            %i.c-icon-normal
            .u-taCenter.p-user_detail-ragtings-score
              0
        %div
          .p-user_detail-ratings.l-clearfix
            %i.c-icon-bad
            .u-taCenter.p-user_detail-ragtings-score
              0
      .p-user_detail-description_box
        %p.c-font-2
          最近メルカリを始めましたので、不慣れなところもありますが出来る限り誠実に取引させていただきます。
          %br
          衣服を中心に出品しますが、当方180センチ、67キロ、タバコは吸いませんり
    .c-item_social-media-box
      %ul.c-social-media-box
        %li
          %a.c-share-btn{"data-window-name" => "facebook_window", :href => "", :target => "_blank"}
            %i.c-icon-facebook
        %li
          %a.c-share-btn{"data-window-name" => "twitter_window", :href => "", :target => "_blank"}
            %i.c-icon-twitter
        %li
          = link_to '', target: '_blank' do
            %i.c-icon-line
    %section.p-item-box_container.l-clearfix.c-items-box_overflow
      %h2.c-items-box_head
        この出品者の商品
      .c-items-box_content.l-clearfix
        - 18.times do
          = render 'layouts/itembox'
